annabis has been reclassified back to class B and the government have sacked a scientificÂ adviserÂ on drugs because he insisted on giving them scientific evidence on drugs.</em></p><div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"><div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-icon sd-sharing"><h3 class="sd-title">Share this:</h3><div class="sd-content"><ul><li class="share-twitter"><a class="share-twitter sd-button share-icon no-text" data-shared="sharing-twitter-110" href="/2002/07/the-hell-of-cannabis-britain/?share=twitter" onclick="__gaTracker(&#39;send&#39;, &#39;event&#39;, &#39;outbound-article&#39;, &#39;http://wasted.dave.org.uk/2002/07/the-hell-of-cannabis-britain/?share=twitter&#39;, &#39;Click to share on Twitter (Opens in new window)&#39;);" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Twitter"><span></span><span class="sharing-screen-reader-text">Click to share on Twitter (Opens in new window)</span></a></li><li class="share-facebook"><a class="share-facebook sd-button share-icon no-text" data-shared="sharing-facebook-110" href="http://wasted.dave.org.uk/2002/07/the-hell-of-cannabis-britain/?share=facebook" onclick="__gaTracker(&#39;send&#39;, &#39;event&#39;, &#39;outbound-article&#39;, &#39;http://wasted.dave.org.uk/2002/07/the-hell-of-cannabis-britain/?share=facebook&#39;, &#39;Click to share on Facebook (Opens in new window)&#39;);" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Facebook"><span></span><span class="sharing-screen-reader-text">Click to share on Facebook (Opens in new window)</span></a></li><li class="share-tumblr"><a class="share-tumblr sd-button share-icon no-text" data-shared="" href="http://wasted.dave.org.uk/2002/07/the-hell-of-cannabis-britain/?share=tumblr" onclick="__gaTracker(&#39;send&#39;, &#39;event&#39;, &#39;outbound-article&#39;, &#39;http://wasted.dave.org.uk/2002/07/the-hell-of-cannabis-britain/?share=tumblr&#39;, &#39;Click to share on Tumblr (Opens in new window)&#39;);" rel="nofollow" targ